=== Loi giai tu luan ===

Thong so: n = 3, k = 2, r = 1
g(x) = x + 1

STT  m(bin)      m(x)           c(bin)
------------------------------------------------------------
0    00          0              000
1    01          x              110
2    10          1              011
3    11          x + 1          101

Ket qua: d_min = 2, phat hien 1 loi, sua 0 loi
